      • findByType

        public <T extends AbstractPreference> Collection<T> findByType(Class<T> clazz,
                                                               String owner)
        Find and return all preferences in the scope of a specific type of Preference and of an owner.

        If owner is set to null or is empty, all preferences of this type are returned. No match returns an empty List ( Collections.emptyList()).

        Specified by:
        findByType in interface ConfigurationService
        Type Parameters:
        T - Any subtype of AbstractPreference
        Parameters:
        clazz - The class of preference to search for
        Returns:
        A Collection of preferences of type T
